text: Romainmôtier-Envy is a municipality in Jura-Nord vaudois in the canton of Vaud in Switzerland. The municipality was created in 1970 by joining together two municipalities, Envy and Romainmôtier.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 19 July 2011 == References == == Other websites == * Official website * Cultural agenda website Category:Municipalities in Jura-Nord vaudois Category:Cities in Switzerland
